data.description: Welcome to this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom split-level home with a 2-stall attached garage in the heart of NW Lincoln. This is your opportunity to enjoy comfortable, modern living with easy access to the interstate and Cornhusker Highway. Bathrooms have been beautifully updated and are ready to pamper you with style and all-new flooring, doors and paint give you the opportunity to step into a fresh and inviting atmosphere. Your dream home is waiting, and it's more affordable than you think. Make it yours today!
